| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7579 — Recovery Inhibition (chaos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 19d8b3cc-5f99-5cee-adee-d9a413b7ae1a"
